CoDefine sim : tm -> tm -> ty -> prop by 
sim M N top := {eval M unit} -> {eval N unit};
sim M N nat := ({eval M zero} -> {eval N zero}) /\
  (forall U, {eval M (succ U)} ->
       (exists V, {eval N (succ V)} /\ sim U V nat));
sim M N (arr S T) := forall MR, {eval M (lam MR)} ->
  (exists NR, {eval N (lam NR)} /\
       (forall x, {of x S} -> sim (MR x) (NR x) T));
sim M N (list T) := ({eval M nill} -> {eval N nill}) /\
  (forall MH MK, {eval M (cons MH MK)} ->
       (exists NH NK, {eval N (cons NH NK)} /\ sim MH NH T /\
            sim MK NK (list T)))
